    protected static class TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.ForSignatureVisitor.OfTypeArgument
extends TypeDescription.Generic.Visitor.ForSignatureVisitor
    Visits a parameter while visiting a generic type for delegating discoveries to a signature visitor.
